{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "A named entity annotated dataset containing 5283 entities and 2161 news phrases is made accessible.",
    "The news texts have been taken from the BBC Urdu website, a helpful source of digital Urdu text (accessed on February 15, 2022 at https://www.bbc.com/urdu).",
    "The most current iteration of the Urdu NER dataset is called UNER-I [72].",
    "CANER dataset [64] The Classical Arabic NER corpus in CANER has been carefully annotated by specialists.",
    "More than 7,000 Hadiths (Prophet Muhammad's sayings) from the Sahih Al-Bukhari book are included in this collection, which uses 21 named object types for annotation where some of these classes are natural object (NatOb), money (Mon), place (Loc), organization (Org), book (Book), measurement (Meas), clan (Clan), crime (Crim), day (Day), number(Num), prophet (Prophet), god (Allah), date (Date), religion (Rlig), time (Time), sect (Sect), hell (Hell), paradise (Para), person (Pers) and others (O)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The most current iteration of the Urdu NER dataset is called UNER-I [72].",
    "CANER dataset [64] The Classical Arabic NER corpus in CANER has been carefully annotated by specialists."
  ]
